\subsection{Characteristic frequencies}
The expressions for nonlinear capacitance indicate that the system has three characteristic frequencies: the frequency $\omega_r$ of mechanical resonance,  the frequency $\omega_\eta$ of viscoelastic roll-off, and the frequency $\omega_{RC}$ of RC roll-off. The limiting values $\omega_{r0}$ and $\omega_{\eta0}$ of, respectively, $\omega_r$ and $\omega_\eta$ have already appeared in Eqs.\ \ref{eq:Cm@m=0} and \ref{eq:Cm-mres}. Those limiting values are asymptotic values for $na \rightarrow 0$. 


